data.description:
This 935 sq-ft home presents an excellent opportunity for all buyers. This cozy residence features 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. The interior boasts tile flooring in the living room, kitchen, and laundry room, creating a seamless and easy-to-maintain living space. 

Convenience meets comfort with an in-house laundry room. The home is equipped with central heating and cooling system to ensure a comfortable atmosphere throughout the year, regardless of the season. 

The exterior of the home is just as appealing with a covered patio in the backyard, ideal for outdoor relaxation or a small gathering. 

This property is priced to accommodate today's market, making it a rare find in the region. Don't miss this chance to own a home in today's market!
